            <mods:abstract>LaSha criticizes one of Beyonce’s biggest critics: Dr. bell hooks. In the article, LaSha references a talk she attended by Dr. hooks, where Dr. hooks went as far as to say Beyonce’s influence makes her a “terrorist.” But LaSha argues that just because a feminist anthem is a commodity, doesn’t mean it is anti-feminist or immoral. This article highlights how everything Beyonce does is examined under a microscope and “hotly debated to polarizing results.”</mods:abstract>
